# Svelte with Routify and Tailwind CSS Template

This is a starter template for building Svelte applications with Routify v3 and Tailwind CSS.

## Installation

To get started, clone this repository:

```
git clone https://github.com/osmancoskun/routify3-tailwind.git
```

Then, navigate into the directory and install the dependencies:

```
cd routify3-tailwind
npm install
```

## Usage

To start a development server, run the following command:

```
npm run dev
```

This will start a development server on `http://localhost:1337` that will automatically reload when you make changes to your code.

To build your application for production, run:

```
npm run build
```

This will create a production-ready build of your application in the `dist` directory.

## Features

This template includes the following features:

- Svelte
- Routify v3
- Tailwind CSS
- PostCSS with Autoprefixer

